data.description: Located on a quiet street just blocks from downtown Sisters, this beautiful home is move-in ready and boasts a highly sought after transferable short-term rental permit! Updated throughout with a comfortable open floorplan, vaulted ceilings & plenty of storage. The large landscaped corner lot offers Cascade mountain views, a fully fenced backyard & hot tub, a detached finished two car garage, covered front porch & extra guest parking. With a private entry to the Owner's Suite, there is opportunity to have two short term rentals.  This home is an excellent investment near parks, trails, shopping, restaurants & coffee shops.
